<div class="col-md-12 mt-3"><marquee behavior="" direction="" onmouseover="this.stop()" onmouseout="this.start()">
    <p class="text-dark font-weight-bold small">
        <span class="badge badge-info fa-1x">Info!!</span> 
        Jika ingin nambah data nota tinggal atau dp pilih tombol <button class="btn btn-white btn-sm font-weight-bold text-dark shadow">Insert</button> | 
        Jika ingin mengedit klik tombol <button class="btn btn-warning btn-sm shadow"><i class="fas fa-pen"></i></button> | 
        Jika ingin menghapus klik tombol <button class="btn btn-danger btn-sm shadow"><i class="fas fa-trash"></i></button> | 
        Jika ingin memasukan data ke nota lunas klik <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm shadow font-weight-bold">Lunas</button> | 
        Jika ingin print QR/Barcode klik <button class="btn btn-white btn-sm shadow text-dark"><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i></button> | 
        Jika ingin detail data lainnya klik <button class="btn btn-white btn-sm shadow text-dark"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i></button> | 
        Jika ingin recovery data nota tinggal klik <button class="btn btn-warning btn-sm shadow"><i class="fas fa-undo"></i></button> | 
        Jika ingin masukan data nota lunas ke laporan klik <button class="btn btn-white btn-sm shadow font-weight-bold text-dark">Report</button> | 
        Jika ingin ambil stok sparepart klik <button class="btn btn-success btn-sm shadow"><i class="fas fa-box-open"></i></button>
    </p>
</marquee></div>